'''Liling Agessy''' (née '''Zedong'''; born July 10, 1957) is a Canadian and American politician, retired marriage counselor and former professional volleyball player. She played for the Vancouver Vans from 1975 to 1989, the Boulder Brownies from 1989 to 1994, and the Detroit Material Girls from 1994 to 1998. 

